snippet.textDisplay:
<!Tu zariya, Hoon main zariya,
Aur uski kirpaa dariya dariya,
Hain jo ankhiya nirmal, 
Duniya nirmal, 
Chhalka chhalka, chhal chhal chhal chhal

You are the medium, So am I, 
and his kindness is vast like a sea.
If your eyes are serene
the world itself will seem serene,

Ho zubaan koi bhi, 
Bol dil se tu bol,
Ya misri si ho, 
Ya shahad si ho.

Language might be any, 
but words should come straight from the heart,
Either it should be like sweet sugar,
Or, sweet as honey.

Wow!! The melodious chorus of girls between crunchy sweet voice of divinely beautiful and immensely talented Farah Siraj is like chocolate cream filling inside a crunchy cookie..... Amazing!!
And Ani Choying ....... what a great find Rahman to bless us indians with!! She doesnt seem to move her lips at all!!!! Yet that amazing spell binding chanting voice beats ALL!!  
Only Rahman, The Indian God of Fusion can bring this MAGIC!!! Gives me goosebumps every time i listen to the song!!
